cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.LG 

The paper deals with the security and monitoring of cyber-physical systems using machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the use of supervised machine learning, which suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper deals with the monitoring of physical systems, which suggests the category cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves the automatic generation of mutants and the use of statistical model checking, which suggests the categories cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
